page: Supreme Court of the United States
message: It seems odd that this lede had no mention of how the Supreme Court came to be.  This info helps a lot when someone is trying to figure out why it's there and what it does.

Switching order.  JFK's moon speech to the joint session of Congress was in May 61, whereas the Berlin Wall started in August of that year.  Also, the NASA rockets were much more closely related to the Cuban Missile Crisis.
JFK inherited the Space Race from Ike.  His salient contribution was setting the goal of landing astronauts on the moon.

/* Soviet response and speech effects */ The fact of his assassination following so closely after his radical pushes for peace should not be ignored.  The Nuke Test Ban Treaty and JFK's reversal on Project Apollo both happened in October '63.
Adding exact quotes from his speech.  He stated he was working toward a comprehensive treaty.  What resulted was a limited treaty.
/* Origins of the term */ Highlighting the fact that Baruch was a key player in the Cold War, added as a parenthetical as this info is an offshoot from the subsection topic.
